name: Create new employees in Deputy from new rows in Google Sheets
description:
This template creates new employees in Deputy based on new rows in Google Sheets. The sample Google Sheets spreadsheet is [here.](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/14_AbZqoPGmkPQso8BCe1yuIXdzVaxGJw9gqMdAkpwHs/edit#gid=0)

The template is scheduled to run every hour. You can change this after you set up the template
